Key Match Events: Shakib Al Hasan scored 64 not out.
Paul van Meekeren took 2 wickets for 15 runs.
Rishad Hossain took 3 wickets for 33 runs.
Engelbrecht scored 33 runs for the Netherlands.
Post-Match Reflections: Bangladesh captain Najmul Hossain Shanto praised Shakib's calmness and the team's character.
Shanto mentioned the good outfield and challenging pitch conditions.
Netherlands' captain Scott Edwards admitted his team was not up to the mark in all three facets of the game.
Edwards acknowledged that Super Eights progression is now out of their hands.
Shakib Al Hasan emphasized the importance of his innings and praised Rishad Hossain for his bowling performance.
